== Events == * {{ill|Shōgen|ja|承元|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|1207|ja|1207|qq=}} {{ill|November 16|ja|11月16日|qq=}} ） – The era was changed from {{ill|Ken'ei|ja|建永|qq=}} to {{ill|Shōgen|ja|承元|qq=}} . * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=}} 14th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1637|ja|1637|qq=}} {{ill|December 11|ja|12月11日|qq=}} ） – The Shimabara Rebellion: Farmers from Amakusa and Shimabara rose against oppressive daimyō and anti-Christian policies. * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=}} 5th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1858|ja|1858|qq=}} {{ill|November 30|ja|11月30日|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Tokugawa Iemochi|ja|徳川家茂|qq=}} ascended as the 14th shōgun. * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1868|ja|1868|qq=}} {{ill|December 8|ja|12月8日|qq=}} ） – Enomoto Takeaki and others occupied the five-pointed star fortress, {{ill|Goryōkaku|ja|五稜郭|qq=}} , in Hakodate.
== Births == * {{ill|Manrei|ja|万暦|qq=}} 20th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1592|ja|1592|qq=}} {{ill|November 28|ja|11月28日|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Hontai-ji|ja|ホンタイジ|qq=}} (皇太極), the 2nd emperor of the Qing († {{ill|1643|ja|1643|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1868|ja|1868|qq=}} {{ill|December 8|ja|12月8日|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Tokutomi Roka|ja|徳富蘆花|qq=}} , a novelist († {{ill|1927|ja|1927|qq=}} ).
