'''October 25''' is the 25th day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October (Lunisolar)|13=User:Immanuelle/Kannazuki|qq=}}  the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}}  day is {{ill|Butsumetsu|ja|仏滅|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Butsumetsu|qq=}} .

== Events ==
* [[:en:Jōgen (Kamakura period)|Shōgen]] 1st year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]]  {{ill|1207|ja|1207|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1207|qq=}}  [[:en:November 16|November 16]] ） – The era was changed from [[:en:Ken'ei|Ken'ei]]  to [[:en:Jōgen (Kamakura period)|Shōgen]] .
* [[:en:Kan'ei|Kan'ei]] 14th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]]  {{ill|1637|ja|1637|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1637|qq=}}  [[:en:December 11|December 11]] ） – The Shimabara Rebellion: Farmers from Amakusa and Shimabara rose against oppressive daimyō and anti-Christian policies.
* [[:en:Ansei|Ansei]] 5th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]]  {{ill|1858|ja|1858|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1858|qq=}}  [[:en:November 30|November 30]] ） – [[:en:Tokugawa Iemochi|Tokugawa Iemochi]]  ascended as the 14th shōgun.
* [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] 1st year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]]  {{ill|1868|ja|1868|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1868|qq=}}  [[:en:December 8|December 8]] ） – Enomoto Takeaki and others occupied the five-pointed star fortress, [[:en:Goryōkaku|Goryōkaku]] , in Hakodate.

== Births ==
* {{ill|Manrei|ja|万暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Manrei|qq=}} 20th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]]  {{ill|1592|ja|1592|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1592|qq=}}  [[:en:November 28|November 28]] ） – [[:en:Hong Taiji|Hontai-ji]]  (皇太極), the 2nd emperor of the Qing († {{ill|1643|ja|1643|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1643|qq=}} ).
* [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] 1st year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]]  {{ill|1868|ja|1868|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1868|qq=}}  [[:en:December 8|December 8]] ） – {{ill|Tokutomi Roka|ja|徳富蘆花|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokutomi Roka|qq=}} , a novelist († {{ill|1927|ja|1927|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1927|qq=}} ).

